Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.73,0:00:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.11,0:01:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空和贝吉塔一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.74,0:01:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在破坏神比鲁斯居住的星球上修炼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.33,0:01:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个人正在挑战维斯布置的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.30,0:01:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,此时，在宇宙遥远的另一端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.76,0:01:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新的威胁蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.68,0:01:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能会危及到地球的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.39,0:02:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，如我所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芭朵斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.44,0:02:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猜错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.28,0:02:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「绝望再现！邪恶帝王弗利萨复活！」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.86,0:02:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来，大家！要开始了喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎，笑一笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.03,0:03:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎，哎，笑一笑嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎，哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.66,0:03:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起笑吧，多开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快报告情况！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！这些是我军的全部兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一第二大队全灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.56,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另外，第三大队也有半数士兵失踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我军已经损失六成兵力吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.57,0:04:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再这样下去不妙，甚至有可能溃不成军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,索尔贝大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事到如今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除了请弗利萨大人复活之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们已经无路可走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让弗利萨大人？复活？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.21,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到那美克星的幸存者了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有，还是没能找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,索尔贝大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,假如弗利萨大人复活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.64,0:04:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他一个人就能改变我军的现状吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.85,0:04:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,塔格玛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.15,0:04:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨大人曾以他不容置疑的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,支配着大半个宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他身为邪恶的帝王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.70,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那残酷无情的形象令整个宇宙畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，就当解解闷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美丽的烟火啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果那位大人复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定能重振我军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.70,0:05:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是弗利萨大人复活后的势力模拟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.91,0:05:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全宇宙的七成范围将被我们支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，事情会那么顺利吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.00,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在质疑我？弗利萨大人去世之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是谁支撑着弗利萨军？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是索尔贝大人您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.55,0:06:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我的计划，我的谋略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.55,0:06:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不必担心，这个计划不会有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.10,0:06:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨大人也一定会赞同我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，去地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，地球不是很危险吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能找到龙珠的那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.53,0:06:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那个打倒了弗利萨大人的赛亚人的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事到如今，你认为我们还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.12,0:06:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,考虑那种事情的余地吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然找不到那美克星人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能冒险前往地球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,调出间谍摄像机的画面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.51,0:06:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能找到龙珠的似乎不只那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.09,0:06:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,塔格玛！我们两个去一趟地球吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.85,0:06:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,索尔贝大人，请让我也一同前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.89,0:06:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,据说地球上的赛亚人不需要用探测器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.10,0:06:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能察觉到强大的战斗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.82,0:06:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去的人多了可能会被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.49,0:07:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是，请原谅我的唐突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如由我和西萨米前往地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,索尔贝大人留在这边是不是更安全？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我怎么能够一直等在这里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.21,0:07:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要亲手复活弗利萨大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.62,0:07:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，停，停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.09,0:07:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然你们两人比以前有进步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是速度仍然不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看，我都来得及签名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你果然厉害啊，维斯先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了，贝吉塔先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.19,0:08:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然你是一个战斗天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.02,0:08:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却总是落后悟空先生一步啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说得真直接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道为什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我哪知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.83,0:08:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你平时一直紧绷着神经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.62,0:08:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以到了关键时刻无法用出全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该放松的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要好好地休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像悟空先生那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.47,0:08:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说得没错啊，贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放松过头也是个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.48,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你对自己太过自信也是个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算再强的人，一旦放松了警惕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身体也会不堪一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在悟空先生身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为太过自信而掉以轻心的情况很常见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.49,0:09:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要这么说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，继续修炼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不见了，不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.75,0:09:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思，比克叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花的时间有点久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟…悟饭，回来得挺快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.67,0:10:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，阿包，谢谢你看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.01,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克叔叔是不是很温柔啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克叔叔，怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.85,0:10:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没注意到吗？那个方向能感应到不祥的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.36,0:10:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.86,0:10:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.15,0:10:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快到了，快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.49,0:10:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，就在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了！修，小舞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊！皮拉夫大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.63,0:10:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就集齐七颗龙珠了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.71,0:10:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今为止经历了多少苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们记得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.68,0:11:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们横渡海洋，翻山越岭，与各种猛兽搏斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.39,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在终于成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.98,0:11:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样一来整个世界就是我皮拉夫大王的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把龙珠交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什什什…什么！你们是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.33,0:11:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要小瞧我们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.08,0:11:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,休想抢走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望你们协助我们一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么能这样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好不容易才集齐的龙珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.37,0:11:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还是不想给他们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我们的啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小舞！不要任性！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.66,0:12:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊！他们绝对是不好惹的家伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在干什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.71,0:12:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.44,0:12:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出来吧，神龙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.57,0:12:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实现我的愿望吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天空变黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.34,0:12:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道，这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是神龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快，说出你的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论任何愿望我都能实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请…请讲吧，无论如何请饶我们一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.91,0:13:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们说不定还有利用价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,索尔贝大人，快许愿吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.96,0:13:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.96,0:13:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.55,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让…让弗利萨大人复活吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.39,0:13:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.35,0:13:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？你不是什么愿望都能实现吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.27,0:13:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是，这个人的肉体已经在很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.86,0:13:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就被切得四分五裂，不能复原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.66,0:14:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只让他的灵魂归体也没有意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下不好办了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使肢体破碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.67,0:14:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要用我军的最新型再生装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说不定还是可以复活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.43,0:14:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨大人的话一定可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.43,0:14:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂！肢体破碎的状态也没关系，快让他复活！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好大的口气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把弗利萨大人复活吧…拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.57,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真没办法，好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.17,0:14:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么再说出剩下的两个愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个愿望？还能实现吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.72,0:15:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，地球的神仙更替的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强化了我的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.47,0:15:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，如果要复活这个星球上所有的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像这种需要花费很大力气的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.06,0:15:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一次就要消耗掉两个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之…之前不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有两个吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.86,0:15:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不让弗利萨大人的爸爸也一起复活吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您问我吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给…给我100万钱币！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想要全世界最好的冰淇淋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.67,0:15:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.17,0:15:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好冷好冷好冷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冰袋是赠品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愿望都实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们这些臭小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我本来还想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后再叫你们帮忙寻找龙珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,索尔贝大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.04,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说不定赛亚人们会赶来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.38,0:16:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是弗利萨大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.17,0:16:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这顽强的生命力加上我军的技术，一定能复原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.57,0:16:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.99,0:16:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你忘了这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.51,0:17:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不久之后我们还会再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.05,0:17:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时会和弗利萨大人以及将士们一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.78,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮拉夫大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个叫弗利萨的究竟是什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.53,0:17:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我怎么知道！反正感觉不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.12,0:17:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们快造艘宇宙船逃到外星去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.83,0:17:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宇宙船…好像造不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是刚拿到了一百万钱币吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该能想出办法吧！干得好啊！修！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你笨啊，怎么不干脆要一亿钱币？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多要一点岂不是更好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你才是！为什么要了冰淇淋啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,融化了不就什么都没了吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.81,0:17:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我一直忍着没买的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.52,0:18:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我什么愿望都没能说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮拉夫大人，总之有了这笔钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.41,0:18:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少暂时不愁吃喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对啊！还有全世界最好的冰淇淋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.37,0:18:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.08,0:18:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，我们先优雅地品尝冰淇淋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后去填饱肚子吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.84,0:18:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.63,0:18:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃了冰淇淋之后吃什么呢，吃什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.59,0:18:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那当然是文字烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消失了，到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有不详的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.44,0:18:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,索尔贝大人，我们总算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在被地球上的赛亚人发现之前完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.28,0:18:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说过了，我的计划不会出问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，我还是有些担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,担心什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对于我军来说，弗利萨大人的复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的有必要吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.91,0:19:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这还用说！当然有必要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自从弗利萨大人和心腹们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被彻底打倒的事情传出去之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我军就开始被轻视了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.30,0:19:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个接一个的星球开始叛乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.43,0:19:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就连我军内部的管理都变得混乱起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.18,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾经远远地看过弗利萨大人一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.44,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么小的身躯看不出有多么强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然我偶尔才能拜见他一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.65,0:19:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我每次都害怕得战战兢兢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.99,0:19:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？万一名不副实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那他只是个虚张声势的独裁者而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说什么没出息的话呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.66,0:19:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,塔格玛！你带着这种软弱的念头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.46,0:19:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么当复活的弗利萨大人的心腹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,西萨米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果弗利萨大人复活，你们就会明白他的强大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.85,0:20:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，复活吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？卡卡罗特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.05,0:20:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么，不知为何我有种不好的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.68,0:20:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要偷懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是错觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.92,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到，我居然会复活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.05,0:21:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邪恶的帝王弗利萨竟然复活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.97,0:21:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对已经身经百战的悟空他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.27,0:21:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨的复仇即将开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.54,0:21:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想当年那一双小手　总难以抱得住的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.25,0:21:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓦然间发现　一转身的我们已长大成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.26,0:21:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,习习微风拂动街角的步伐　多么想乘上风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.30,0:21:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（新的故事开始）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.31,0:22:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来　是时候起程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,STARRING STAR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.35,0:22:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一瞬间铺天盖地点亮　今夜像奇迹一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.32,0:22:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,念念在心间且长此以往　是珍贵无比的温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.28,0:22:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,STARRING STAR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.45,0:22:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪一天漫天星光倾泻　聚集像珠落玉盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.21,0:22:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么　到时候的星辉　一定会比现在强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.46,0:22:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.88,0:22:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家好，我是悟天
